otherFacts.value: Sprinklers In Front, Master Planned, Foothills

data.description: Move into your dream without waiting for your home to be built! This gorgeous home is the largest Horizon View floorplan and the only one in the Raindance Community currently! Home is lightly lived in at only 8 months old. Throughout you will find gorgeous white cabinets and white granite with clean LVP flooring. The master and laundry are on the main and other bedrooms separate in the upper level. You will love looking over your backyard at a clear view of those gorgeous Colorado mountains and the Colorado Cherry Company right in your backyard! Backyard is not complete, but seller is offering a $5,000 concession for you to make it your own oasis. First two years of water park free for residents of Raindance and this home sits only 2 blocks away. Do not wait to live in this amazing master planned community!
